### Sprint 8: Knowledge Consolidator Worker - Testes de Integração

### 1. Health Check do Sistema
GET http://localhost:8000/readyz
Accept: application/json

###

### 2. Adicionar Experiência de Teste na Memória Episódica
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/experience
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "O agente utilizou a ferramenta de busca web para pesquisar sobre FastAPI. A API retornou resultados relevantes sobre documentação oficial e boas práticas de desenvolvimento assíncrono.",
  "type": "tool_usage",
  "metadata": {
    "tool": "web_search",
    "query": "FastAPI best practices",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T14:30:00Z",
    "outcome": "success"
  }
}

###

### 3. Adicionar Outra Experiência de Teste (Erro)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/experience
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "Tentativa de conexão com Neo4j falhou após 3 retries. O banco de dados retornou timeout error. O sistema acionou o circuit breaker e utilizou fallback.",
  "type": "error",
  "metadata": {
    "component": "Neo4j",
    "error_type": "ConnectionTimeout",
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T14:35:00Z",
    "retry_count": 3
  }
}

###

### 4. Adicionar Experiência sobre Relacionamentos
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/experience
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "O sistema implementou o padrão Circuit Breaker para proteger a conexão com Neo4j. O LLM Manager utiliza Ollama como fallback quando OpenAI falha. Prometheus coleta métricas de todos os componentes.",
  "type": "system_architecture",
  "metadata": {
    "patterns": ["circuit_breaker", "fallback", "observability"],
    "components": ["Neo4j", "LLM Manager", "Prometheus", "Ollama"],
    "timestamp": "2025-10-06T14:40:00Z"
  }
}

###

### 5. Buscar Experiências na Memória Episódica
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/memory/search
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "Neo4j circuit breaker",
  "n_results": 5
}

###

### 6. Acionar Consolidação de Conhecimento (Sprint 8 Worker)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/knowledge/consolidate
Accept: application/json

###

### 7. Verificar Entidades Criadas no Grafo
GET http://localhost:8000/api/v1/knowledge/entities
Accept: application/json

###

### 8. Consultar Experiências Consolidadas no Neo4j
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (e:Experience) RETURN e.id, e.timestamp, e.consolidated_at LIMIT 10"
}

###

### 9. Visualizar Entidades Extraídas (Conceitos/Tecnologias)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (n) WHERE n:CONCEPT OR n:TECHNOLOGY OR n:TOOL RETURN labels(n)[0] as type, n.name as name, n.last_seen LIMIT 20"
}

###

### 10. Visualizar Relacionamentos Extraídos
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (a)-[r]->(b) WHERE NOT a:Experience RETURN type(r) as relationship, a.name as from, b.name as to, r.source_experience LIMIT 20"
}

###

### 11. Consultar Insights Armazenados
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (e:Experience) WHERE e.insights IS NOT NULL RETURN e.id, e.insights LIMIT 5"
}

###

### 12. Verificar Padrão MENTIONS (Experiência -> Entidade)
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (e:Experience)-[:MENTIONS]->(n) RETURN e.id, labels(n)[0] as entity_type, n.name as entity_name LIMIT 20"
}

###

### 13. Buscar Experiências Relacionadas a uma Tecnologia Específica
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (tech {name: 'Neo4j'})<-[:MENTIONS]-(e:Experience) RETURN e.id, e.type, e.timestamp"
}

###

### 14. Estatísticas do Grafo de Conhecimento
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/system/query-graph
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "MATCH (n) RETURN labels(n)[0] as type, count(*) as count ORDER BY count DESC"
}

###

### 15. Métricas Prometheus (Consolidação)
GET http://localhost:8000/metrics
Accept: text/plain

# Buscar por:
# - knowledge_consolidation_total
# - knowledge_entities_extracted_total
# - knowledge_relationships_created_total
# - knowledge_consolidation_latency_seconds

###
